    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《草人扎针》是一款射击类型的小品游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以射出大头针在旋转的固定标靶上，注意避开已经占位的大头针，并且射入对应大头针颜色的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将每一关限制的大头针数量成功插上标靶，点燃蜡烛，即可通关！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.webm?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/c28316c0f82e95e05f5fbc059a80fb8d.mp4?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色🪡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14种充形状各异的标靶</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2种射击类型 + 2种型态的大头针</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >21个关卡可以挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30~50分钟的游戏时间</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99c6a26a1dea51b9da383f.poster.avif?t=1745773383\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259810/extras/25981e1cef99c6a26a1dea51b9da383f.mp4?t=1745773383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
